---
title: Szechuan Style Beef Noodles with Mushrooms
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Szechuan Style Beef Noodles in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/15-c2c57dd8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/6581bd63f9c7ff868993d78b.pdf
